snoopy.blindnote: This snoRNA is the human orthologue of the mouse MBII-295 described by Htenhofer et al. (2001). It has no identified RNA target. (20100708末安)snoRNABaseを参考にsequenceを5'側から4nt短くした,NCBIを参考にaccession Noを加えた,UCSCを参考にgenomic positionを変更した,evidenceはsnoRNAbaseのレファレンスから抜粋。
snoopy.evidence: Huttenhofer, A., Kiefmann, M., Meier-Ewert, S., O'Brien, J., Lehrach, H., Bachellerie, J. P., and Brosius, J. (2001). RNomics: an experimental approach that identifies 201 candidates for novel, small, non-messenger RNAs in mouse. Embo J 20, 2943-2953.
